---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="页面未找到"
  description="请求的页面不存在。请返回首页浏览澳洲百科的全部条目。"
>
  <div class="max-w-editorial mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
    <p class="chapter-num text-aus-green text-4xl mb-4">404</p>
    <h1 class="font-heading text-2xl text-aus-ink font-bold mb-4">页面未找到</h1>
    <p class="text-aus-muted mb-8">您请求的页面可能已被移除，或从未存在。</p>
    <a href="/" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-aus-red text-white rounded-sm font-heading no-underline hover:bg-aus-green transition-colors">返回首页</a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
